    "description": "<strong>Get ready for the ultimate power couple's co-op crusade in this explosive top-down action game!</strong><br>Unleash your inner fighter and join forces with your partner to seek vengeance and reclaim your children in a thrilling revenge story. Inspired by the intense combat of <strong>Hotline Miami</strong> and Kill Bill, this game will have you at the edge of your seat as you battle through the Sakamoto tower filled with enemies.<br><br>But what sets this game apart is its emphasis on unique co-op movements that will leave your jaw dropping. With an incredible focus on men-women relationships, this game blends serious tones with dark humor and meta-jokes. The neo-noir vibes and cinematic visuals of this game's unique top-down perspective with 3 visible levels will transport you to a world like no other.<br><br>Are you ready to team up and fight for what's yours in this epic couple's co-op crusade?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369380/extras/f292c36127693c94fc0c9d353e8b4b64.webp?t=1680856873\" width=594 height=17 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369380/extras/c75f4483a117a11891177ff7df520a82.poster.avif?t=1680856873\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369380/extras/c75f4483a117a11891177ff7df520a82.webm?t=1680856873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369380/extras/c75f4483a117a11891177ff7df520a82.mp4?t=1680856873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
